{
  "meta": {
    "name": "Tactical Decision-Making Curriculum",
    "version": "5.0.0",
    "description": "10-stage curriculum (0-9): navigation → target selection → pheromone → repellent → fog → AoE flanking → AoE spread → combined arms → screening → randomized. MultiDiscrete([8, 2500, 4]) action space with CNN+MLP feature extractor."
